This paper discusses the accuracy of face recognition algorithms, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also addresses issues related to bias and fairness, which are relevant to the computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with image processing and analysis, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
